snippet: The French authorities canceled the rest of the Trophée Bompard, a Grand Prix event in Bordeaux, because of the terrorist attacks in Paris.
abstract: Trophee Bompard, international figure skating event in France, is canceled due to terrorist attacks in Paris.
lead_paragraph: The French authorities canceled the rest of the Trophée Bompard, a Grand Prix event in Bordeaux, because of the terrorist attacks in Paris.
